            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>Gen</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>g</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aeus</ex></expan> Firmininus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>onius</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost">v</supplied>itus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Firmini<lb break="no" n="6"/>us Veruic<lb break="no" n="7"/>i<supplied reason="lost">us</supplied> <expan><abbr>Mar</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Vi<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>dilla <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elia</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Vivia <expan><abbr>Dom</abbr><ex>itia</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>Iu<supplied reason="lost">sta</supplied> qui <lb n="11"/>pro <supplied reason="lost">se et</supplied> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">suis omnib(us)</supplied> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Altar ist im Grundriß sechseckig. Auf einer Seite des Mittelteils befindet sich die Inschrift auf den fünf anderen Darstellungen Iuppiter, Iuno, Minerva, Diana und Hercules. Z. 3 nach Dolenz vermutlich nachträglich eingefügt.</p>
            </div>
